\f1\b\fs40 \cf0 GOD
\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f2\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Up to this point the nation of Israel had really messed things up and they had felt stuck for a long time\'8540 years in fact!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}40 years of roaming a desert helplessly and hopelessly feeling as though they have no control over their future.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They were in this predicament because they messed up\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They did the wrong things\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They committed the wrong sins\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But their biggest sin was that they didn\'92t trust God with an opportunity\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And because of that they wandered the desert for 40 years.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Stuck and out of control\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Relegated to an average mundane life\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf4 The things that God over and over exalts are not perfect people but people that pursue Him (work on this statement)\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f2\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Here is what I want you to see though\'85we\'92re going to pick up the story after God has reminded them of all of their past mistakes and sins and here is what God says\'85\
