\f3\b \cf5 \super 22\'a0
\f2\b0 \nosupersub If you carefully observe\'a0all these commands I am giving you to follow\'97to love\'a0the\'a0Lord your God, to walk in obedience to him and to hold fast\'a0to him\'97\'a0
\f3\b \super 23\'a0
\f2\b0 \nosupersub then the\'a0Lord\'a0will drive out\'a0all these nations\'a0before you, and you will dispossess nations larger and stronger than you.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The nations and the people didn\'92t get an smaller!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Sometimes we want to wait for the obstacle to get small and then we\'92ll move but that isn\'92t how God works.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Many times we don\'92t move because the obstacle seems bigger than the opportunity!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But I\'92ve realized that size is all relative to how close I am to the object.  \
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
