\f1\b\fs28 \cf3 Transition:  A few verses later he clarifies it for them so they know exactly what God is offering them\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs24 \cf5 \super 26\'a0
\f2\b0 \nosupersub See, I am setting before you today a blessing\'a0and a curse\'97\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I love this because God clarifies there are only two ways to live life\'85blessed or cursed.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The problem is as I said earlier many of us have compromised so much the curse just feels normal and we\'92re ok with it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But here is what I want you to see more than anything\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b \cf5 \super 27\'a0
\f2\b0 \nosupersub the blessing\'a0if you obey the commands of the\'a0Lord\'a0your God that I am giving you today;\'a0
\f3\b \super 28\'a0
\f2\b0 \nosupersub the curse if you disobey the commands of the\'a0Lord\'a0your God and turn from the way that I command you today by following other gods,\'a0which you have not known.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f4 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God looks at his people who had messed up over and over again and says\'85IF!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s is in your hands \'96 IF\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Blessing or Curse\'85you\'92re call\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Your past is irrelevant to your future\'85IF\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God puts all the power and control back into the hands of His people and says choose!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We are not helpful, hopeless, and out of luck about our futures and our lives.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We have complete control and we are not stuck\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We get to choose what our futures will be!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs28 \cf0 \uc0\u8232 
\f5\b \cf3 Transition:  So what does this look like in my life?\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs40 \cf0 YOU\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\f4\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We\'92re going to be talking about it over the next several weeks but it starts with the simplest of tasks\'85\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This will be the simplest to understand; yet hardest to follow through with assignment I ever give.  Wake up every morning, first thing (before Facebook, coffee, everything) and ask God, what do you want me to do today?  And then do it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}(Explain how to do this clearly for those who are far or don\'92t know God)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This one decision can radically change your life in a big way\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I know what some are thinking?  What about my addiction, how is that going to help with my finances, what about my marriage problems.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can\'92t pursue sin and God at the same time.  And again, your job is to be faithful to what God tells you to do\'85period!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f5\b\fs28 \cf3 Transition:  So here is what I\'92m asking you to do today:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0
\f4\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Make a decision to live the life God has called you to do and believe in the power of IF\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
